                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check2 text-accent me-2"></i>Generate previews and metadata for your organizational needs.</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check2 text-accent me-2"></i>Transmit content via secure links at your explicit request.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

