                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-x-circle me-2 text-danger"></i>Upload illegal, pirated, or infringing materials.</li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-x-circle me-2 text-danger"></i>Attempt to breach the security or integrity of our systems.</li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-x-circle me-2 text-danger"></i>Use the platform for spamming, phishing, or malware distribution.</li>
                                <li><i class="bi bi-x-circle me-2 text-danger"></i>Exceed reasonable bandwidth or storage limits as defined by your plan.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-5">
